T1  - Control as an Organizational Process
AU  - Haberstroh, Chadwick J.
Y1  - 1960/01/01
PY  - 1960
DA  - 1960/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.6.2.165
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.6.2.165
